307
00:26:11,009 --> 00:26:13,178
Dia ada dimana-mana, Lorelei.

308
00:26:13,386 --> 00:26:17,807
Dia punya mata dan telinga di mana-mana.

309
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:22,646
Tunggu…

310
00:26:26,358 --> 00:26:29,986
Mulut John masih bergerak
dalam video.

311
